    <body>
      <div>
        <head xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e14">1. Na togalaichean: sobhal, bàthach is mar sin, agus ainm gach pàirt dhiubh</head>
        <entry xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e19">
          <form>
            <orth>airidh</orth>
          </form>
          <def>hen roost.</def>
        </entry>
        <entry xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e28">
          <form>
            <orth>atha</orth>
          </form>
          <def>equiv. of ‘sobhal’.</def>
        </entry>
        <entry xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e37">
          <form>
            <orth>àth</orth>
          </form>
          <def>kiln.</def>
        </entry>
        <entry xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e46">
          <form>
            <orth>aol</orth>
          </form>
          <def>lime.</def>
        </entry>
        <entry xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e55">
          <form>
            <orth>slacadh</orth>
          </form>
          <def>slackening the lime. Slacke [sic] – adding water.</def>
        </entry>
        <entry xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e64">
          <form>
            <orth>ath cheilp</orth>
          </form>
          <def>kelp kiln.</def>
        </entry>
        <entry xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e73">
          <form>
            <orth>ath aol</orth>
          </form>
          <def>lime kiln.</def>
        </entry>
        <entry xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e82">
          <form>
            <orth>tireadh</orth>
          </form>
          <def>grinding. Drying of the grain in the barn.</def>
        </entry>
      </div>
      <div>
        <head xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e90">2. A’ mathachadh no a’ leasachadh na talmhainn</head>
      </div>
      <div>
        <head xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e94">3. A’ treabhadh no a’ ruamhar: an crann agus ainm gach pàirt dheth</head>
      </div>
      <div>
        <head xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e98">4. Innealan beaga leithid spaid, gràp, ràcan is mar sin</head>
      </div>
      <div>
        <head xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e102">5. Acfhuinn an eich airson gach seòrsa obair</head>
      </div>
      <div>
        <head xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e106">6. A’ cur an t-sìl</head>
      </div>
      <div>
        <head xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e110">7. A’ buain agus a’ tiormachadh an arbhair no an fheòir</head>
      </div>
      <div>
        <head xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e114">8. A’ togail a’ bhuntàta</head>
      </div>
      <div>
        <head xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e118">9. A’ tasgadh an arbhair agus a’ bhuntàta</head>
      </div>
      <div>
        <head xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e122">10. A’ bualadh ’s a’ criathradh</head>
      </div>
      <div>
        <head xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e126">11. A’ bleith an t-sìl</head>
      </div>
      <div>
        <head xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e130">12. Ainmean a chleachdar ri earrainn fearainn</head>
      </div>
      <div>
        <head xml:id="AssortedFieldworkers_AnonymousBaiteach-d0e134">13. Faclan sam bith eile</head>
      </div>
    </body>
